从而进行视频、音频、图片的大屏播放，打造真正的数字生活网络联盟。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t451/71/316308346/262294/3e0bf485/545c92aeN698f9cf0.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    D11系列贴心自带谷歌浏览器，高效、简洁、迅速，支持网址收藏，支持html5在线播放，类似电脑浏览器一样的畅快上网体验。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t532/129/296376077/338819/db88979a/545c9374N74153b02.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">    如你所知，电视机主要通过屏幕向我们展示世界，因此，是否拥有出众的画质才是衡量一台电视好坏的关键标准。TCL自然光技术通过光路创新，将液晶电视发出的线偏振光转化成圆偏振光，这种技术可以带来三个好处：一是降低电视功耗，更环保；二是保护眼睛，不易疲劳；三是让色彩自然，画质优异。</div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t595/324/293228604/333598/65f3e520/545c93e2Na9b9b282.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">TCL特有的鹦鹉螺音箱系统，仿生学设计，应用了隐形磁悬浮专利技术和气悬浮处理技术，让机体音效立体饱满，极其接近原音。</div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-17\" name=\"detail-tag-id-17\" text=\"产品展示\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <span>产品展示</span>\n    <span class=\"s2\">Products Exhibition</span>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t634/52/310599179/154961/2778c41b/545c9490Ncb19c424.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t559/332/305712180/212981/44fe71c0/545c9545N9e1ce332.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><div class=\"formwork\">\n<div class=\"formwork_img\"><img src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/jfs/t550/66/471863393/306400/64f01ebd/545c9556Nfadb8f3a.jpg\" /></div>\n</div><html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"formwork_bt\" id=\"detail-tag-id-21\" name=\"detail-tag-id-21\" text=\"品牌介绍\">\n   <div class=\"formwork_bt_dz\">\n    <s